Package co.lokblok.toughkeylib

Class TKObject

java.lang.Object
co.lokblok.toughkeylib.TKObject
public class TKObject extends Object
Represents a data object stored on the Toughkey device. This class provides a representation of a data object, including its label, value, length, and permissions.
